---
const PORTRAIT = 'https://ozxbjwvwchesjgebenbv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/media/7d299b9c-50c1-4675-a5ef-49bce505d803.webp';
---
<section class="maker">
  <div class="maker__grid">
    <div class="maker__portrait">
      <img src={PORTRAIT} alt="Delvin Begay — portrait" />
    </div>
    <div class="maker__body">
      <div class="maker__eyebrow">◆ Meet the maker</div>
      <h2 class="maker__title">Meet the <em>maker.</em></h2>
      <p class="maker__lede">
        I'm so glad you're here. My love for turquoise, silver, and the desert
        crashed headfirst into a dream called Tacky Turquoise.
      </p>
      <p class="maker__body-copy">
        I grew up in the high desert outside Gallup, New Mexico. Every stone I set
        is hand-cut and hand-strung by Navajo and Zuni silversmiths I know by
        first name. I'm fur-mom to two dogs, a few too many horses, and one
        stubborn rabbit. My pieces are loud, heavy, one-of-a-kind, and
        made to be passed down.
      </p>
      <p class="maker__body-copy">
        I'm so thankful for each and every one of you for making this dream
        real.
      </p>
      <div class="maker__sign">
        <span class="verse">Joshua 1:9</span>
        <span class="dash">—</span>
        <span class="name">Ash</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
